caption:
I’m forever grateful to @lydiabottelier for introducing be to Doce Taqueria in South Side, Pittsburgh 👏🌃🌮

@docetaqueria has quick and affordable food options that are made fresh when you order! My go-to order is the box special, which includes two tacos 🌮🌮 and chips with your choice of salsa 🍅, guac 🥑, or queso 🧀! It’s a great deal that’s perfect for lunch or a late night snack. There’s also tons of other options to choose from (@jordann.carrier, AKA @philadelphiafoodgirl got the bowl) that are all customizable! They even have tons of hot sauce to spice things up 🌶️🌶️🌶️

Stop by Doce Taqueria next time you’re in South Side, where your mouth and your wallet will be happy! 😄💃🌮
